_sText: IMPORTANT Its important to link the map for FASTDOWNLOAD! Its impossible to download files with Steamgames that are BIGGER THAN 15MB (such as this map is). Otherwise player can NOT download it. [[ Missing map dialog ]] For sound and those things you need "sv_pure 0" If you want to DISABLE THE MUSIC and so on just enter the server var "sv_pure 1" The entertainment in this map Every spawn has a spray written "KAM!KAZE mapped here" on it. Press on that "here" to play some music. The music ends when it usually ends (up to 4minutes) but the button just resets after 5 minutes. In fact of that the music wont be spammed. Its not too loud, so you can hear enemy players steps. CREDITS [MUSIC] Showtek ----------------- Colors Of Hardstyle Dark Oscillators --------- Stereophobia Headhunterz vs Abject -- Scantraxx Rootz PS: If you think that the map is like every aim_deagle then you are pretty wrong. Just try. Playing 5hours a week on that map will make you better. RECOMMENDED: Play the map on: Deathmatch Headshot Only Noblock (Friendlyfire off) (20-30 minutes till mapchange)
